 Galvatron raised his mechanacal eyebrow. "Wow that was impressive. He shot 
out his wings and jetesoned upwards.  He was much larger then the bot do to 
his dragon mode and was easy to move out of the way of such a small full body 
blast. He stared down the bot. Waiting for him to make the next move. This 
bot must be a new comer. It was not in his databanks of the known bots from 
Apoicalypse or any of the dna strains he had collected. He thought of his  
Ability from his taken DNA. The dna he took from Zadus would come in handy 
now.  Unfortunatly it could onlt work in best mode. He had yet to try it but 
he wanted to see how it would take the energy blast. He powered up and a 
armor with a sligt blue color covered his body. He had taken the quality of 
Zardus's impressive armor. Though adapted to Galvatron's body had the smae 
stength and endurance. With a little power boost. He awaited the bots 
approach.
